text: Phoebe spegazzinii is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Bruch in 1908. It is known from Argentina, Brazil and Paraguay.BioLib.cz - Phoebe spegazzinii. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1908
title: Phoebe spegazzinii
